  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:0",
      "text": "Workspace tab 主要是一个 viewer，用于显示与你的 asset management policies 相关的 preferences 和 variables 的 settings 与 values。",
      "ascii_letters": 75,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:1",
      "text": "你可以在这里使用 tokens 定义 output naming，甚至通过 pipeline 以及 User Names and Values 来自动化它们。这是一种便捷的 shorthand，可用于定义 naming conventions，无需把内容输入成长字符串，并允许 token 根据 project settings 自动 resolve，而不需要 user interaction。",
      "ascii_letters": 112,
      "cjk_chars": 57
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:2",
      "text": "RenderMan for Maya 可以在 string parameters 中替换若干 predefined tokens。它们可用于 animated texture sequences、引用特定 storage locations 等。",
      "ascii_letters": 88,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:6",
      "text": "Scene name",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:8",
      "text": "Maya Render Layer name",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:10",
      "text": "Render camera name",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:12",
      "text": "AOV 或 LPE name",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:14",
      "text": "会将 AOVs 写入 named sub-directories",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:16",
      "text": "Frame padding，此处为 4；可省略表示 no padding，或使用较小数字",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:18",
      "text": "File type extension",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:20",
      "text": "Maya 当前 workspace，即 project 中的 file path",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:22",
      "text": "插入上方指定的 version number",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:24",
      "text": "插入上方指定的 take number",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:26",
      "text": "Current date",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:27",
      "text": "<assetlib>",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:28",
      "text": "指向 standard RenderMan Asset Library 的 Path",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:30",
      "text": "Scene file name",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:32",
      "text": "Decimal frame number",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:34",
      "text": "Unique job identifier",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:36",
      "text": "Short shape name（所有 instances 具有相同 shape name）",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:37",
      "text": "<shapepath>",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:38",
      "text": "Long shape name（所有 instances 都有唯一的",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:39",
      "text": "shapepath names，用于完整路径标识）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:41",
      "text": "Current time",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:43",
      "text": "UDIM identifier（仅在 render time 替换）",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:44",
      "text": "<imagedir>",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:45",
      "text": "包含完整的 image output directory 路径",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:47",
      "text": "Generic texture atlas identifier",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:48",
      "text": "（仅在 render time 渲染时替换）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:49",
      "text": "Environment Variables",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:50",
      "text": "Environment variables 必须以 $ sign 开头，并且只能使用 capitals、numbers 和 \"_\" characters：",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:51",
      "text": "：返回 txmake utility 的 path。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:52",
      "text": "Curly braces 也可以用于 composition：",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:53",
      "text": "Retrieving attribute values",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:54",
      "text": "RfM 不再支持 TCL expression，但允许 attribute evaluation：",
      "ascii_letters": 35,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:55",
      "text": "返回 shape node 上 'time' attribute 的 value（'shape'，而不是 'transform' node）。",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:56",
      "text": "也可以通过指定 formatting string 来 format numerical attribute values：",
      "ascii_letters": 46,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:57",
      "text": "：如果 time attribute 的当前 value 是",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:61",
      "text": "Python 标准格式化说明符（python's standard format specifiers）",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45a00d667d:63",
      "text": "由于 tokens 是 shorthand，你可能希望在 rendering 前查看它们会 resolve 成什么。你会看到 eye icon。选择它会显示 token choices 得到的 resulting strings。",
      "ascii_letters": 66,
      "cjk_chars": 31
    }
  ],
